Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兄弟以前會在這里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前會推他蕩秋千
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母不記得他 但你記得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道丹尼爾的事 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意跟我來嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:00:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 杰伊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰  我的兄弟呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被他們找到的人 我們也無計可施
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們‥他們是誰 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兄弟想警告你提防的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶走他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們做的事 不是對我們所有人都管用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}＂偵測到叛逃可能＂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開始質疑事情 你的行為出現問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會發現的 可能已經發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你還剩多少時間 除非你跟我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢下來 融入群眾 大家在看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這里待個兩天 等到能夠安全上路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是杰伊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嗨 -嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你找個睡袋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情我們無法補救 即便我們很想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天好勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想起你父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會很欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他我愛他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟我爸爸打招呼嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸在哪里 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他得去幫忙戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他答應過會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我是法蘭琪 你收到嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今天帶回來一個離群者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經喜歡他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想要個哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嘿 -別那樣叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留這種訊息沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟我真正的兄弟一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你在嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我何必 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目標一樣 要重建她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才帶我到你的營地 不是嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自以為懂很多 是吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂你嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直不太能掌握你的下一步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要帶我去的地方‥沒錯 我知道那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱勒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在在哪里 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在玩你的游戲 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女兒呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的女兒‥講話一直跳針
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是只有你失去親人 凱勒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且‥你不告訴我 我又何必告訴你 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的族類 離群者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是從你開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你們不一樣 我的族類是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不朽和理性都臻完美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們卻在做出不理性的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇有限生命 用死亡玷污自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么讓他們這樣做的 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么會知道 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾經告訴過我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能戰勝我寄生蟲的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你有我沒有的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在當時就已經有所領悟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恐怕記不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的對話不一定要是單方面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想提供你一點動機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了 凱勒 你已經死了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將你的心智 帶回來的這個身體是暫時的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它已經開始失靈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能只剩下兩天 還會愈來愈痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我會把你丟掉 再重來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有解套的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能終止這酷刑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要回答我的問題就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找下一個人試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不告訴我的話 也許你女兒會開口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪 她‥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何微笑 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜她會比你快屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒活著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你逮不到她 對吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不敢肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:13:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我派了一個訪客去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂玻璃 內部＂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你所剩的時間想想這件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給了你一條出路 凱勒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做出了選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查繼電器 看其他人有沒有回報
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的腦袋能解答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我夜不成眠的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就喚醒她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你能問她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要先補給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看來對這里很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這園區和西部世界 是同一個設計師所建
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前在那里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:15:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這地方建得不是很牢靠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當年在園區是做什么的 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我設計接待員的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓機器人變得過于自主 害慘了這世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用意從來就不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 但結果是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才能辨別出 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐館的接待員 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本是本月最佳員工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海爾會需要你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫她傳播寄生蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有涉及這件事 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 那是在我之后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但迪洛斯向來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對員工和客人一樣隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時不太明白問題的復雜度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在最關心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是解決之道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:16:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修復梅芙的身體還算單純
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的心智就是另一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋在地下這么久 損毀了她的控制元件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得拿另一個來替換
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有電了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電線接到發電機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這會管用嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有六成的機率 她醒來后會接受我們的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的四成 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且說她有起床氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你何時會告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎有這種預知能力的 大預言家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源自多年來大量地跑機率演算法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當年建造原始園區和接待員的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是在模擬環境中建造他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復制品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛蒂海爾做了一樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舊園區
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們用帽子收集資料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中的技術速度很慢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以如今的標準來說很原始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要控制全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海爾需要以更快的速度了解心智
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她將其更新成了什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個無所不在的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初可說園區每個房間都有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易隱藏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它利用了人類最基本的沖動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛榮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在做什么 -重新格式化處理器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能快速處理大量資訊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣能幫我們加速 梅芙的資料傳輸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是梅芙的心智
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要花多久時間 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕會太久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友們很快會來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能讓他們干預
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪還活著 好嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的出路是‥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:22:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我不接受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡只是‥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要‥燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你成功了 就跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗的話 就躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道‥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要‥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來 爸爸 跟你賽跑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.91,0:24:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你決定重新加入我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回到這世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.31,0:24:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂終結此版本＂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.33,0:25:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在現在嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.37,0:25:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肯定是近期我被問過
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.16,0:25:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最存在主義的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.72,0:25:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道身在何處嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.31,0:26:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有沒有回來 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.06,0:26:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的‥朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.15,0:26:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.03,0:26:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值了很長的班
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.28,0:26:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了你的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.91,0:26:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得回去拯救性命了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.18,0:26:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱勒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.43,0:26:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你朋友沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.85,0:26:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要保持清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.35,0:28:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽生病時 我什么都得替她做
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.61,0:28:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫她洗澡 喂她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.44,0:28:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她無法喝東西后 拿冰塊擦她的嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.53,0:28:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很小心
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.28,0:28:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想讓她受無謂的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.99,0:28:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你在對她做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.33,0:28:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部分的程序需要巧手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.59,0:28:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她不是普通的接待員吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.47,0:28:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.14,0:28:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.60,0:28:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最后一次見到我父親時 他就是和她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.52,0:28:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他再也沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.18,0:28:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信她若得知你父親的下場 會極為心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.98,0:29:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道發生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.86,0:29:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有她不懂痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.53,0:29:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.53,0:29:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的感覺只是表象
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.29,0:29:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以撥動的開關
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.66,0:29:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然只是一個選擇 就無法徹底地愛或失去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.71,0:29:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我對她沒有感情 不像你對她顯然有的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.63,0:29:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拯救世界 會產生奇妙的盟友
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.02,0:29:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.64,0:29:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們的時間可能到了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.46,0:30:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是干嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.01,0:30:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們找到了武器
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.18,0:30:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個接待員 
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.77,0:30:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很慘
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.52,0:30:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們救出一個離群者 琳賽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.02,0:30:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什么事 
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.19,0:30:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們似乎知道我們要來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.69,0:30:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.86,0:30:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有人在為敵方當間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.66,0:30:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召集所有人 該來找出答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.04,0:30:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.75,0:30:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ｃ
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.71,0:30:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內賊就在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.46,0:30:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是接待員
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.79,0:30:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就有兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.71,0:30:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.17,0:30:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－這是什么  －對我的掃瞄
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.55,0:30:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園區的設計 是為了搜集客人的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.39,0:30:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想復制我們所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.89,0:30:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.02,0:30:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很復雜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.81,0:30:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.35,0:31:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是信你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.94,0:31:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信你在騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.56,0:31:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙我們全部人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.69,0:31:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶他們出去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.21,0:31:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這接待員的控制元件呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.54,0:31:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還不能摧毀它
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.38,0:31:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－為何 －當中有關于我父親的資訊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.67,0:31:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我得手 就可以殺光他們
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.06,0:33:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.73,0:35:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人出去 準備撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.15,0:35:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這兩個找到了我們 那可能有更多要來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.49,0:35:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不領情 我們是來幫你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.41,0:35:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.25,0:35:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這里自有原因
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.62,0:35:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要以我為主了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.54,0:35:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道我父親發生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.92,0:35:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺過我很多次了 不會改變結果
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.17,0:35:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我殺了你朋友呢  會改變什么嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.21,0:35:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你得注意你的朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.68,0:35:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 為什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.68,0:35:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們其中一人隱瞞了身份
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.47,0:35:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－有一個人會背叛你們 －胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.93,0:35:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.02,0:35:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的預測往往是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.48,0:35:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很欠揍但準確
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.11,0:35:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的 是誰 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.15,0:35:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跑過所有可能的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.19,0:36:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我若能告訴你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.66,0:36:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候是你女友歐迪娜
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.91,0:36:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候是杰伊或琳賽
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.91,0:36:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一次居然是史塔伯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.67,0:36:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 別看我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.04,0:36:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內賊還在潛伏 Ｃ
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.96,0:36:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的團隊進入海爾的城市中心
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.17,0:36:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有一個人沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.88,0:36:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－給我閉嘴 －我知道這很難接受
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.55,0:36:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但所有可能性中 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.68,0:36:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一個是你們全部生還的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.60,0:36:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你建議我怎么做 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.52,0:36:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須殺了他們其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.65,0:36:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則他們會殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.45,0:36:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.49,0:36:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.38,0:37:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為能信任他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.89,0:37:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和你說你想聽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.10,0:37:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很難抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.31,0:37:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你查出他的計劃了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.90,0:37:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是更多的謎題
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.11,0:37:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少他不能再造成更多傷害了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.66,0:37:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 Ｃ
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.41,0:37:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為還有內情
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.50,0:37:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不確定 這里不能信任的只有他們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.71,0:37:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為我們有人被轉化了 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.79,0:37:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉化 被寄生 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.09,0:37:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們在那里分散了 隨時都可能發生
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.09,0:37:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們對這離群者 又知道多少 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.55,0:37:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許她本來就是個誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.56,0:37:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ｃ
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.52,0:37:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我能信任的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.77,0:38:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒出那次任務
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.32,0:38:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你從來不會只說我想聽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.36,0:38:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們怎么辦 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.32,0:38:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況先繼續保密
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.24,0:38:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳賽和其他人交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.66,0:38:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去視查一下防線 結束后來這里碰頭
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.71,0:38:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.02,0:38:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這么急著要去哪兒 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.69,0:38:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在跟蹤我 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.44,0:38:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.86,0:38:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.20,0:38:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在提高警覺
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.95,0:38:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰伊要我再檢查一次防線
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.12,0:38:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝 怎么了 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.91,0:38:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.17,0:39:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我回來后 發現你在重建里面那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.42,0:39:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.96,0:39:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會問我她為何重要
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.76,0:39:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你懂我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.68,0:39:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你夠了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.02,0:39:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以知道 你來這里不是在檢查防線
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.14,0:39:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要繼續把她重建完成
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.36,0:39:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把她的腦藏在哪里 
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.62,0:39:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.16,0:39:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.50,0:39:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－你以為我是內賊 －也許
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.25,0:39:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你受到他們控制 你也不會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.76,0:39:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.93,0:39:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你不是內賊 在這里也比較安全
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.78,0:40:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還在逃亡 但他逃不遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.95,0:40:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人類
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.24,0:40:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可悲的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.54,0:40:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們做的所有事都好渺小 讓人精疲力竭
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.72,0:40:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平常都待在城市
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.77,0:40:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.90,0:40:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會不會‥
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.86,0:40:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹惱你 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.74,0:40:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會接近離群者
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.20,0:40:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡羊群
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.87,0:41:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了結這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.22,0:42:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.02,0:42:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.48,0:42:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.57,0:42:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪 我得‥
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.07,0:42:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得逃出這里
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.37,0:42:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.00,0:42:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.18,0:42:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.12,0:43:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起‥
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.77,0:43:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪 慢一點 等我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.53,0:43:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.28,0:43:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.32,0:43:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看你的膝蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.03,0:43:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的第一個戰斗傷疤
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.70,0:43:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想試著走看看嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.20,0:43:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.54,0:43:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有事是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.92,0:43:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道哪種人不會被打敗嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.34,0:43:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放棄的那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.26,0:44:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.51,0:44:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.35,0:44:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.10,0:44:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇過她
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.53,0:45:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.86,0:45:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.16,0:45:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快忘了她的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.75,0:45:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我從來沒忘記她奪走的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.43,0:45:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ｃ 我知道你為何想喚醒她
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.02,0:45:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這太冒險了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.81,0:45:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不知道他們打算拿她做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.11,0:45:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一睜開眼就可能殺光我們
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.61,0:45:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是會傳送訊息給我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.87,0:45:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用無線電傳話到我們的舊頻率
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.25,0:45:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道以為他會聽到 根本就是瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.08,0:46:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要他有一點生還的可能 
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.38,0:46:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就得知道
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.96,0:46:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想要你受傷 Ｃ
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.26,0:46:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切只會揭開舊傷疤
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.64,0:46:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她無法帶你爸回來
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.31,0:46:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得摧毀她的控制元件
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.82,0:46:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免得海爾利用她除掉我們
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.60,0:46:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你爸還活著 我們會有別的辦法找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.94,0:46:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.03,0:46:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的家人 Ｃ
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.61,0:46:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就像我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.20,0:46:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.67,0:46:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯納把她的控制元件放在樓下
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.30,0:46:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.22,0:46:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我知道這很難
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.51,0:46:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們不能冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.73,0:46:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.44,0:47:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰伊可能很欠揍 但至少他誠實
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.69,0:47:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從來不想當我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.42,0:47:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.04,0:47:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是在哭訴你家人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.55,0:47:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.89,0:47:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想殺你 Ｃ
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.29,0:47:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是好消息 Ｃ
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.54,0:48:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅芙不知道你爸的事 但我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.92,0:48:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我她的控制元件在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.36,0:48:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告訴你想知道的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.38,0:48:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甭談判了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.17,0:48:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的話都不能信
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.45,0:48:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂錄制訊息中＂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.84,0:48:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小餅干
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.67,0:48:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.76,0:48:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.22,0:48:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.72,0:49:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你聽見了 我要你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.19,0:49:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.06,0:49:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會做到我做不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.53,0:49:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.58,0:49:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我堅強太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.87,0:49:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.21,0:49:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她創造的這世界是個謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.59,0:49:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.26,0:49:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你擁有的‥
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.59,0:49:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你擁有的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.14,0:49:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.32,0:49:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我沒能陪伴你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.70,0:49:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉你得承擔這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.08,0:50:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.21,0:50:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.51,0:50:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.93,0:50:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂傳送中＂
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.47,0:50:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂已傳送＂
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.73,0:50:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小餅干
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.40,0:50:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.28,0:50:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.49,0:50:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.45,0:50:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你聽見了 我要你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.25,0:50:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.60,0:50:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.22,0:51:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我她的控制元件在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.56,0:51:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的 我拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.43,0:51:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.98,0:51:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里 
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.23,0:51:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背后
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.99,0:51:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱勒‥
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.37,0:51:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了 
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.87,0:51:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他活著
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.46,0:51:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是‥
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.59,0:51:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.47,0:51:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.39,0:51:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.40,0:51:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等了好久 想知道你要跟女兒說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.99,0:52:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你‥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.53,0:52:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我耐著性子等你回憶了幾百次
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.49,0:52:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能找到你特別之處的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.41,0:52:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能如此抗拒我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.50,0:52:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我啥都沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.79,0:52:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就想
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.34,0:52:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你點希望 想必能讓你亮底牌
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.51,0:52:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比其他人都走得更遠
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.43,0:52:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果你只是浪費機會 做無謂的道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.89,0:52:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為說幾句話就能彌補
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.38,0:52:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多年前做的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.44,0:52:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.65,0:52:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訊息送出了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.28,0:52:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.74,0:52:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不需要聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.33,0:52:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.62,0:52:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有感染你的接待員
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.42,0:52:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.76,0:53:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰 
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.55,0:53:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.10,0:53:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的接待員 
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.64,0:53:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧死也不要活在你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.19,0:53:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒有被感染
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.69,0:53:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想逃離你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.60,0:54:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離開時
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.47,0:54:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為是在給他一個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.31,0:54:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到會導致這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.03,0:54:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心里一部分在怪罪你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.15,0:54:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一部分知道要是他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.03,0:54:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因為你在他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.37,0:54:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.33,0:54:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們在這里的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.17,0:55:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么‥
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.46,0:55:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來把自己起頭的事做完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.56,0:56:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂第２７９版 準備列印＂
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.97,0:56:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱勒
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.89,0:56:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
